      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="469-0271" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Written in the Year 1729.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi>N Ass's Hoof alone can hold</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-2"> That pois'nous Juice which kills by Cold.</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-3"> Methought when I this Poem read,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-4"> No Vessel, but an Ass's Head,</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-5"> Such frigid Fustian could contain;</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-6"> I mean the Head without the Brain.</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-7"> The cold Conceits, the chilling Thoughts,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-8"> Went down like stupifying Draughts:</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-9"> I found my Head began to swim,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-10"> A Numbness crept through ev'ry Limb:</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-11"> In Haste, with Imprecations dire,</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-12"> I threw the Volume in the Fire:</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-13"> When, who could think, tho' cold as Ice,</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-14"> It burnt to Ashes in a Trice.</l></lg><lg n="2" type="stanza"><l n="15" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-15">H<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">OW</hi> could I more enhance its Fame?</l><l n="16" xml:id="spp-469-0271-line-16"> Though born in Snow, it dy'd in Flame.</l></lg></div>
      </div>
